{"name": "odoo-addon-product-lst-price-calculate", "metadata": {"name": "odoo-addon-product-lst-price-calculate", "version": "15.0.1.0.0.3", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 15.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/sygel-technology/sy-product-attribute", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Calculate product sales price according to cost and expected margin", "upload_time": 1734518149}, "documentation": ["```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.svg\n:alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n:target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl\n```\n\n# Product Lst Price Calculate\n\nThis module allows to calculate at which price a product should be sold according to its cost and expected profit margin.\n\n## Installation\n\nTo install this module, you need to:\n\n1. Only install\n\n## Configuration\n\nTo configure this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go to Sales > Configuration > Settings > Pricing and activate the \"Apply Product Min. Margin\" option when the product profit margin needs to be equal or greater than a given value.\n2. Go to Sales > Configuration > Settings > Pricing and set a value in the \"Product Margin Calculation Default (%)\" field to use this rate as the default calculation rate.\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use this module, you need to:\n\n1. Go to a product template or variant form view.\n2. Modify the followin values in order to calculate the price at which the product should be sold:\n   : 1. Sale Price Calculation\n     2. Vendor Price Calculation\n     3. Vendor Discount Calculation\n     4. Theorical Margin Calculation (%)\n3. Click on the 'Transfer' button next to the 'Sale Price Calculation' value to set this value as the product sales price.\n4. In case the company has the \"Apply Product Min. Margin\" option activated, it will be checked whether the Theorical Margin Calculation rate is equal or greater than the set value.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs and errors are managed in [issues of GitHub](https://github.com/sygel-technology/sy-product-attribute/issues).\nIn case of problems, please check if your problem has already been\nreported. If you are the first to discover it, help us solving it by indicating\na detailed description [here](https://github.com/sygel-technology/sy-product-attribute/issues/new).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Sygel, Odoo Community Association (OCA)\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Manuel Regidor \\<<mailto:manuel.regidor@sygel.es>>\n\n### Maintainer\n\nThis module is maintained by Sygel.\n\n```{image} https://www.sygel.es/logo.png\n:alt: Sygel\n:target: https://www.sygel.es\n```\n\nThis module is part of the [Sygel/sy-product-attribute](https://github.com/sygel-technology/sy-product-attribute).\n\nTo contribute to this module, please visit <https://github.com/sygel-technology>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models", "documentation": ["Copyright 2024 Manuel Regidor <manuel.regidor@sygel.es>", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models.product_product", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models..product_product", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models.product_template", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models..product_template", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models.res_company", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models..res_company", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models.res_config_settings", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.product_lst_price_calculate.models..res_config_settings", 